{"tid":2451980,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"均益大廈三期完成強檢　約1800名居民檢測沒確診","createTime":"2021-03-18T13:06:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T13:06:19.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"98b9a21554b2530f070f8dc15fd1320ffe788be1","tid":2451980,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T13:06:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581198-20210318.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581198-20210318.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2UcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=2117d78f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581198-20210318.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=0742a9a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581198-20210318.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n西營盤德輔道西均益大廈第三期上午約7時完成強制檢測行動，截至凌晨2時，大約1800名居民接受檢測，當中沒有發現確診個案。<br />\n<br />\n自上午約7時起，「受限區域」內已進行檢測的人士，如能出示陰性檢測結果電話短訊或配戴手環以證明接受強制檢測，可在向人員提供個人資料後，經由指定出口離開。<br />\n<br />\n政府在「受限區域」內派員到訪大約775戶，當中約70戶沒人應門，包括一些確診個案和可能已經接受隔離的住戶，亦有可能部分單位是空置，會採取措施跟進。"}]}